{"id":460,"date":"2019-03-01T22:07:02","date_gmt":"2019-03-01T22:07:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/?page_id=460"},"modified":"2019-03-06T19:23:03","modified_gmt":"2019-03-06T19:23:03","slug":"mastercard-more-priceless-time","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/mastercard-more-priceless-time\/","title":{"rendered":"Mastercard: More Priceless Time"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2>How do you position a premium credit card to time-poor French professionals?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube alignfull wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/1OT3QreAOSI?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube alignfull wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/qbAajDw8gR0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube alignfull wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/tExjZHmcBc8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/METRO-iStock_98964293_XXXLARGE.jpg\" alt=\"Mastercard: More Priceless Time is a TV &amp; Social Media Campaign that ran in Western Europe to promote travel with MasterCard. It encourages people to get out of their comfort zone and to easily try new things thanks to their personal concierge who can help organise your life. I was responsible for concept development and art direction on this project.\" class=\"wp-image-461\" srcset=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/METRO-iStock_98964293_XXXLARGE.jpg 3000w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/METRO-iStock_98964293_XXXLARGE-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/METRO-iStock_98964293_XXXLARGE-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/METRO-iStock_98964293_XXXLARGE-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/METRO-iStock_98964293_XXXLARGE-1568x1045.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p>With a campaign that focuses on fun things you can be doing while your personal assistant organises your life.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because\n in an age of Apple\u2019s Siri, Google Now and Amazon\u2019s Alexa, there\u2019s still\n nothing as reliable and useful as a living, breathing, human assistant.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p>This campaign ran as YouTube pre-rolls &amp; Video-On-Demand, with \nresults that over-indexed the category average. This was helped by an \nA\/B test and learn approach on our call to actions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:0\">\/\/A \ud83d\udcb3<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>How do you position a premium credit card to time-poor French professionals? With a campaign that focuses on fun things you can be doing while your personal assistant organises your life. Because in an age of Apple\u2019s Siri, Google Now and Amazon\u2019s Alexa, there\u2019s still nothing as reliable and useful as a living, breathing, human [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/460"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=460"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/460\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":749,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/460\/revisions\/749"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=460"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}